            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿الْمُزْنِ﴾ السَّحَابِ.</h2>"
        },
        "70": {
            "verses": {
                "56:70": {
                    "id": 70
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿أُجَاجًا﴾ شَدِيدَ المُلُوحَةِ؛ لاَ يُنْتَفَعُ بِهِ فِي شُرْبٍ، وَلاَ زَرْعٍ.</p>"
        },
        "71": {
            "verses": {
                "56:71": {
                    "id": 71
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿تُورُونَ﴾ تُوقِدُونَ، وَتَقْدَحُونَ الزِّنَادَ لاِسْتِخْرَاجِهَا.</p>"
        },
        "72": {
            "verses": {
                "56:72": {
                    "id": 72
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أَنْشَأْتُمْ﴾ أَوْجَدْتُّمْ.</h2>\n<p>﴿شَجَرَتَهَا﴾ الشَّجَرَةَ الَّتِي تَقْدَحُ مِنْهَا النَّارُ؛ كَالمَرْخِ والعَفَارِ.</p>"
        },
        "73": {
            "verses": {
                "56:73": {
                    "id": 73
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿تَذْكِرَةً﴾ تَذْكِيرًا لَكُمْ بِنَارِ جَهَنَّمَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَمَتَاعًا لِلْمُقْوِينَ﴾ مَنْفَعَةً لِلْمُسَافِرِينَ.</h2>"
        },
        "74": {
            "verses": {
                "56:74": {
                    "id": 74
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿فَسَبِّحْ بِاسْمِ رَبِّكَ﴾ نَزِّهْ رَبَّكَ ذَاكِرًا اسْمَهُ.</p>"
        },
        "75": {
            "verses": {
                "56:75": {
                    "id": 75
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿فَلاَ أُقْسِمُ﴾ أُقْسِمُ وَأَحْلِفُ، وَ(لاَ): تَوْكِيدٌ لِلْقَسَمِ.</p>\n<p>﴿بِمَوَاقِعِ النُّجُومِ﴾ بمَسَاقِطِهَا فِي مَغَارِبِهَا فِي السَّمَاءِ.</p>"
        },
        "76": {
            "verses": {
                "56:76": {
                    "id": 76
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>...</p>"
        },
        "77": {
            "verses": {
                "56:77": {
                    "id": 77
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿كَرِيمٌ﴾ عَظِيمُ المَنَافِعِ، كَثِيرُ الخَيْرِ، غَزِيزُ العِلْمِ.</p>"
        },
        "78": {
            "verses": {
                "56:78": {
                    "id": 78
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مَكْنُونٍ﴾ مَسْتُورٍ مَصُونٍ.</h2>"
        },
